data.description: Discover your perfect home! This inviting 5- bed,  3- bath home is move- in- ready. As you pass through the covered front patio you are welcomed in to a bright and open concept. With 3 bedrooms on the main level and 2 upstairs, you are sure to have enough space for everyone! One of the bedrooms upstairs is oversized and could make the perfect den or playroom. The dining and living area open to a screened deck that offers a retreat from Alabama sun! The whole- home generator and storm shelter (that fit up to 10 people), ensure safety, while the cul-de-sac location provides a secure and friendly environment. Receive the “new build” feel without the wait and hassle of building. A few other things to love about this home: Luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout (no carpet), gas stovetop, CUSTOM closets, upgraded quartz countertops, upgraded landscaping with concrete sidewalk and extended patio, and a fenced yard. There is no much more to appreciate but you will have to see for yourself!
